--
-- Global variables
isBag = false
isObj = false

pos = {x={0.00}, y={2}, z={8.58}}
--posDrop = {0,2,8.58}
zoneObj = '997592'
zoneBag = '82818a'
zoneResult = 'ecd040'
bagDespenser = 'ce7e45'


function f_copyScript()
    testPads()

    if isBag and isObj then
        process()
        broadcastToAll("****** COPY COMPLETE ******", "Yellow")
    else
        broadcastToAll("****** ERROR ******", "Red")
    end

    isBag = false
    isObj = false
end

function getScript()
    return testZoneObj()[1].script_code
end

function process()
    local script = getScript()
    local copyBag = getCopy()

    prams = {position = {0.00, 1.13, 8.57}, rotation = {0,180,0}}
    local b = getObjectFromGUID(bagDespenser).takeObject({})
    b.setRotation(prams.rotation)
    b.setPosition(prams.position)

    pos = {x=0.00, y=1.13, z=8.57}
    local Y = 6
    local cloneBag = copyBag.clone({})
    local objList = cloneBag.getObjects();
    for _, obj in pairs (objList) do
        local c = cloneBag.takeObject({})
        local rot = c.getRotation()
        --c.setPosition({pos.x, Y, pos.z})
        c.setRotation(rot)
        c.script_code = script
        b.putObject(c)
        Y = Y + c.getBounds().size.y + 0.5
    end
    cloneBag.destruct()

end

function testPads()
    --BAG test
    --print(tostring(#testZoneObj()))

    if #testZoneObj() == 1 then isObj = true
    else broadcastToAll('Only have 1 object on source to copy scripts from', 'Orange') end
    if #testZoneBag() == 1 then isBag = true
    else broadcastToAll('You need to have a single bag of objects you wish to copy the script to!', 'Orange') end
end

function testZoneObj()
    local zoneContents = getObjectFromGUID(zoneObj).getObjects()
    local sourceList = {}

    for _, obj in pairs(zoneContents) do
        if obj.guid != '27da79' then
            table.insert(sourceList, obj)
        end
    end

    return sourceList
end

function testZoneBag()
    local zoneContents = getObjectFromGUID(zoneBag).getObjects()
    local sourceList = {}
    for _, obj in pairs(zoneContents) do
        if obj.tag == 'Bag' then
            table.insert(sourceList, obj)
        end
    end
    return sourceList
end

function getSource()
    local zoneContents = getObjectFromGUID(zoneObj).getObjects()
    sourceList = {}

    for _, obj in pairs(zoneContents) do
        if obj.guid != '27da79' then
            table.insert(sourceList, obj)
        end
    end

    if #sourceList == 1 then
        run = true
        return sourceList[1]
    else broadcastToAll('Only have 1 object on source to copy scripts from', 'Orange') return false end

    return false
end

function GET(loc)
    local zoneContents
    if     loc == 'source' then zoneContents = getObjectFromGUID(zoneSource).getObjects()
    elseif loc == 'target' then zoneContents = getObjectFromGUID(zoneTarget).getObjects()
    elseif loc == 'result' then zoneContents = getObjectFromGUID(zoneResult).getObjects() end


end

---------------------- MAKE BUTTON CODE -----------------------------

function makeButtons(set)
    local buttons = {}

 -- DEFAULT START BUTTONS
    if set == nil then
        local button = {
                click_function = 'f_copyScript',
                function_owner = self,
                label = 'Copy Scripts',
                position = {0, 0.5, 0.5},
                rotation = {0, 180, 0},
                width = 2500,
                height = 350,
                font_size = 200}
        table.insert(buttons, button)
    end
 -- Create Buttons
    for _, button in ipairs(buttons) do
        self.createButton(button)
    end
end



function onload()
    makeButtons()
end

-- Remove Name? (EDIT THIS TO TRUE IF YOU WANT)
RemoveName = false
RemoveDescription = false

-- Global variables

zoneBag = 'aca898'
zoneResult = 'ecd040'
bagDespenser = 'ce7e45'


function f_copyScript()
    testPad()

    if isBag then
        process()
        broadcastToAll("****** SCRIPT REMOVAL COMPLETE ******", "Yellow")
    else
        broadcastToAll("****** ERROR ******", "Red")
    end

    isBag = false
end


function process()
    local copyBag = getCopy()
    local Y = 6
    --Get New Bag
    prams = {position = {0.00, 1.13, 8.57}, rotation = {0,180,0}}
    local b = getObjectFromGUID(bagDespenser).takeObject({})
    b.setRotation(prams.rotation)
    b.setPosition(prams.position)

    local cloneBag = copyBag.clone({})
    local objList = cloneBag.getObjects();

    for _, obj in pairs (objList) do
        local c = cloneBag.takeObject({})
        local rot = c.getRotation()
        c.setRotation(rot)
        c.script_code = ''
        if RemoveName then c.setName('') end
        if RemoveDescription then c.setDescription('') end
        b.putObject(c)
        Y = Y + c.getBounds().size.y + 0.5
    end
    cloneBag.destruct()
end
